1. Arrays are of fixed size
2. The size of an array has to be defined at the time of instantiation.
3. Every Array has a 0 based index
4. methods to work with Arrays (perform CRUD operations)
5. An exception is raised when a non exitent element is accessed
6. the type for an array can be primitive or object type.

7. Syntax
   <Datatype>[] <variable_name> = {comma seperated values};
